      "type": "wysiwyg",
      "name": "WYSIWYG",
      "settings": {
        "text": "<h5><strong>VISIT OUR DISTILLERY!<\/strong><\/h5><p>Stop in for the Bourbon and stay for the atmosphere! Desert Ghost embodies the spirit of the borderlands, and you’ll see that spirit come to life in our tasting room and our community. From locals who have spent their whole lives here in Marathon, to Big Bend visitors and international tourists and celebrities, we take pride in welcoming every person who comes through the door. You never know who will be on the barstool next to you, but we’re pretty sure you’ll leave as friends! There is just something about sipping bourbon in the desert that connects people, and that is one more reason we love this town and our distillery.<\/p>",
        "button_url": "",
        "button_label": ""
      }
    },
