          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "THERE'S ALWAYS SOMETHING HAPPENING AT DESERT GHOST",
            "text": "<p>It’s hard to find live music out here in the middle of the desert, but we are fortunate enough to have a good rotation of local singer-songwriters and bands to satisfy your live music needs. If you’re someone who wants to be in the spotlight, we also offer karaoke on select nights. Kids and well-behaved dogs are always welcome too! <\/p>",
